85 contract period or periods.
86 3.(3) Nothing in this article shall be construed to
87 confer continuing service status on any participating teacher.
88 The contract term for a participating teacher shall not count
89 toward accrual of continuing service status."
90 Section 2. This act shall become effective on October
91 1, 2026.
